WEBVTT

09:15.090 --> 09:16.850 line:80%
down the stairs at noon.

09:17.160 --> 09:17.880 line:80%
Look.

09:18.400 --> 09:20.190 line:80%
He lost two front teeth.

09:20.190 --> 09:21.800 line:80%
Tell me,
what are you going to do about it?

09:21.800 --> 09:23.530 line:80%
My sister has always been weak.

09:23.650 --> 09:26.180 line:80%
Your grandson is years older than her.
